# CodeRabbit CLI

Use CodeRabbit as a way to review code. It is available in the terminal as `cr`.

## Commands

- List options: `cr -h`
- **Default for uncommitted changes**: `coderabbit --prompt-only -t uncommitted`
- Always use the `--prompt-only` flag when running CodeRabbit.

## Limit

When reviewing a given set of changes, **do not run CodeRabbit more than 3 times**.
